text: Galesville is a census-designated place (CDP) in Anne Arundel County, Maryland, United States. As of the 2020 census, 623 people lived here. Galesville is at 38°50'35" north, 76°32'37" west (38.8431707 -76.5435702). == References == Category:Census-designated places in Maryland Category:Anne Arundel County, Maryland
